<!-- Project Header -->
<section class="project-header">
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold">Churn Analysis</h1>
        <p class="lead">Predicting customer attrition and identifying retention strategies using survival analysis and machine learning</p>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Project Overview -->
<section class="container mb-5">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-8">
            <h2 class="section-title">Project Overview</h2>
            <p>This abalysis walks through solutions to tackle customers churn through useing machine learning techniques.  This was achieved through using features such as subscription patters, engagement metrics, and other demographic data.</p>
          
           
            <h3 class="mt-4">Business Objectives</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Identify key factors and behavioral patterns that lead to customer churn</li>
                <li>Develop a predictive model to identify customers at high risk of churning</li>
                <li>Estimate potential revenue savings from improved retention</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4">
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Technologies Used</h5>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <span class="badge bg-primary skill-badge">Python</span>
                        <span class="badge bg-primary skill-badge">Pandas</span>
                        <span class="badge bg-primary skill-badge">NumPy</span>
                        <span class="badge bg-primary skill-badge">Matplotlib</span>
                        <span class="badge bg-primary skill-badge">Seaborn</span>
                        <span class="badge bg-primary skill-badge">Scikit-learn</span>
                        <span class="badge bg-primary skill-badge">Lifelines</span>
                    </div>
                    
                    <h5 class="card-title mt-4">Techniques</h5>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <span class="badge bg-primary skill-badge">Survival Analysis</span>
                        <span class="badge bg-primary skill-badge">Kaplan-Meier Estimation</span>
                        <span class="badge bg-primary skill-badge">Cox Proportional Hazards</span>
                        <span class="badge bg-primary skill-badge">Random Forest</span>
                        <span class="badge bg-primary skill-badge">Feature Importance</span>
                        <span class="badge bg-primary skill-badge">Customer Lifetime Value</span>
                    </div>
                    
