            <div class="row mt-4">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="text-center">
                        <img src="static/images/churn/churn_by_age.png" alt="Churn by Age Group" class="img-fluid viz-img">
                        <figcaption class="text-muted mt-2">Churn rate by age group, showing higher churn among younger customers (18-24) and older customers (65+).</figcaption>
                    </div>
