            <p class="card-text">Customer lifetime value (LTV) in relation to churn provides insights into financial impact of retention efforts.</p>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="text-center">
                        <img src="static/images/churn/ltv_by_churn.png" alt="LTV by Churn Status" class="img-fluid viz-img">
