                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4">
                <h5>LTV Analysis Insights</h5>
                <ul>
                    <li>Retained customers have 2.8x higher LTV compared to churned customers</li>
                    <li>Premium subscribers who churn still have higher LTV than retained Basic subscribers</li>
                    <li>The financial impact of reducing churn is highest for Premium customers</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
